data.description: OPEN HOUSE SATURDAY, NOVEMEMBER 11TH 12PM - 2PM. Welcome to Luxury Living in the Heart of Oak Creek.  Nestled within the prestigious Oak Creek Community in Upper Marlboro, Maryland, this stunning residence offers the epitome of modern elegance and comfort.  Situated amidst lush landscapes and scenic views, this home combines upscale living with the tranquility of a tight-knit community.  Step inside and be greeted by an expansive 2 story foyer that seamlessly connects the large living room.  The living room flows to the dining area where you will love entertaining during the holidays.  Make your way to the heart of this home, the beautifully appointed kitchen. It boasts granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, ample cabinet space, and a generous island that's perfect for casual dining or entertaining.  Beyond the kitchen is a gorgeous cathedral ceiling sunroom with large windows that flood the space with natural light, creating an inviting ambiance.  Off the kitchen you find the enormous family room.  Enjoy the outdoors on the expansive maintenance free deck overlooking the beautiful backyard backing to trees.  It's an ideal place for al fresco dining, barbecues, or simply relaxing in the sun.  The main level includes a half bathroom and laundry room.  Making your way to the upper level you will find the primary suite offering a true retreat with a spacious bedroom, 2 walk-in closets, and a luxurious en-suite bathroom complete with his/her sinks, a soaking tub and separate shower. Three additional bedrooms provide plenty of space for family and guests.  Another hall bathroom on this level. The basement offers a versatile space for game room, fitness area, and is a perfect spot for hosting movie nights or game day gatherings.  Additional space available to build out a theatre room or 5th bedroom.  Rough-in for full bathroom already set up.  As an added bonus the property has solar panels to help keep those energy bills down saving you money. Oak Creek Community offers a plethora of amenities including a championship golf course, swimming pool, clubhouse, walking trails, and more. It's a lifestyle that's second to none. This home provides easy access to major commuter routes, shopping centers and dining options.  Washington, D.C. is just a short drive away, making it a great choice for commuters. Don't miss this opportunity to make Oak Creek your new home. Schedule a showing today and experience the epitome of luxury living in Upper Marlboro, Maryland.
